Package ch.iserver.ace.net.discovery.dnssd

The package ch.iserver.ace.net.discovery.dnnsd contains classes specific to the discovery implementation, which is domain name system service discovery (DNSSD).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Browse DNSSDCall implementation for a DNSSD browse call.
QueryRecord DNSSDCall implementation for a DNSSD query record call.
Register DNSSDCall implementation for a DNSSD register call.
Resolve DNSSDCall implementation for a DNSSD resolve call.
RetryStrategyFactory Factory to create instances of a RetryStrategy implementation.
TXTUpdate DNSSDCall implementation for a DNSSD TXT update call.
 

Exception Summary
DNSSDCallException Application exception.
DNSSDUnavailable Exception thrown if a DNNSD call failed after the service recovery strategy (RetryStrategy failed.
RetryException Exception thrown if a retry strategy failed.
